file.name: AudienceManager.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
AudienceManager:
  type: object
  description: Audience Manager Integration (AAM).
  properties:
    locationHint:
      type: integer
      minimum: 1
      description: |
        DCS location hint.
        Used to determine which AAM DCS Endpoint to hit in order to retrieve the profile.
    blob:
      type: string
      minLength: 1
      maxLength: 1024
      description: |
        AAM Blob. Used to send additional data to AAM.
        Validation
          * Cannot be blank.
